{"tid":1235654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【求反送中肉麻窩心小故事】同700萬+1香港人share","createTime":"2019-06-17T08:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T15:36:05.000Z","uid":263378,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"481c773ff8f89c424825e4b2855318e60eeaf45a","tid":1235654,"uid":263378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:01:55.000Z","msg":"<strong>有人說，香港自從2019年的6月開始，變得不一樣。</strong>有班社工見到大家呢幾日有好多香港人<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>義載﹑義印、mtr車長叫乘客加油</strong></span>之類的事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢哋係fb開咗個page俾大家share呢啲窩心小故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> <strong>做個記錄，俾善忘嘅香港人記得自己肉麻過</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴打絲打<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇稿供</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E7%AA%A9%E5%BF%83%E5%B0%8F%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B-430755330842723/?modal=admin_todo_tour\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25AA%25A9%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2595%2585%25E4%25BA%258B-430755330842723%2F%3Fmodal%3Dadmin_todo_tour&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0uy%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=781dce61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E7%AA%A9%E5%BF%83%E5%B0%8F%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B-430755330842723/?modal=admin_todo_tour</a>"},{"pid":"e34f0457f0a5fadd1b049e28d697b567accc5f51","tid":1235654,"uid":263378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:45:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EqD6LBN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEqD6LBN.jpg&h=4c8999e5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n6月12號，諗起傘運個陣，夏愨道中間石壆啲樓梯"},{"pid":"d23c60b2d85ad07d09052ef2762d718d36b93cea","tid":1235654,"uid":263378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:51:05.000Z","msg":"【繼續求窩心故事】<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#1<br />\n<br />\n深夜搭的士回住處，司機先是苦惱表示，到處封路，好難兜，又問：「點解留到咁遲？」<br />\n<br />\n「我係記者呀嘛。」<br />\n<br />\n「蛤，你邊間架？」<br />\n<br />\n「台灣飛過來架。」<br />\n<br />\n「咁你星期三係唔係度？」<br />\n<br />\n「唔係度，好可惜。」<br />\n<br />\n「係呀。果日呢，我接到姑姐電話，話我表弟同幾百個同學都去晒金鐘，要我拉佢返黎。我表弟係果啲鍾意本民前、本土果種，老實講我覺得呢一代人好激進。咁我咪打俾我表弟，點知佢話，你咁大架車，不如幫我車返啲物資過黎呀，我啲好急住要呀。咁幫咪幫咯，搬左成四箱生理鹽水過去，我先知原來今次出來好多都係女仔，仲要好細個。我見佢地咁細粒，咪話幫佢地搬啲物資上去物資站，點知個女仔就話，Uncle呀，你冇裝備唔安全呀，我啲去啦。果一刻我真係好慚愧。點解而家啲女仔咁大膽呢？」<br />\n<br />\n「個女仔保護番你，咪幾好。你係咪都好感動呢？」<br />\n<br />\n「係呀。」<br />\n<br />\n「呢度轉左呀，唔該。」<br />\n<br />\n「好，係咪呢度落？」<br />\n<br />\n「係呀係呀，唔該。同埋呢，多謝你幫返你表弟，而冇拉佢番去。」<br />\n<br />\n「都多謝你呀，記者朋友。拜拜啦。」"},{"pid":"ddfa8587b55253149d014202675574fa7eeb9a8b","tid":1235654,"uid":34602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:52:35.000Z","msg":"唔好鍋我個心得唔得&hellip;&hellip;我有咩得罪你"},{"pid":"06e3960d8ea89b02611ac73db781b4abf45b7faf","tid":1235654,"uid":263378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T12:07:32.000Z","msg":"唔係有心窩大家嘅，但重要嘅嘢要記低，第日區選/大家心灰意冷時攞返出黎，唔係大家會唔記得的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#2<br />\n<br />\n2019-06-16<br />\n<br />\n表揚有心人❤️<br />\n<br />\n1. 準備去遊行, 等車寫住示威牌先<br />\n剪緊紙皮，狼狽之際，後面個叔叔話：&quot;不如我幫你拎住你剪啦&quot;， 就出手同我一齊整。<br />\n之後我分咗半塊紙皮俾佢，一人整咗一塊示威牌 ，yeah! <br />\n<br />\n2. 等咗九個字，未上到車，過海巴士全淪陷。<br />\n忽然有人揸架7人車來巴士站：「我可以載六個！」<br />\n<br />\n太感動，香港和香港人😭"},{"pid":"c98d28837bf484707cadde940445562e8feb9412","tid":1235654,"uid":263378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:36:05.000Z","msg":"#3<br />\n<br />\n2019-06-16<br />\n<br />\n今天有許多第一次遊行的年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n我們幾個街坊整咗張超大的白布banner，正愁唔夠人手拉，一邊行一邊叫沿途市民幫手。有兩個後生仔過黎拉，原來係第一次行的，冇準備任何示威道具，咩都冇得做又好似有啲不知所措，之後就幫我哋拉banner拉咗全程。<br />\n<br />\n仲有個後生仔，傍晚時分急急腳離開，原來係冇話俾家人知黎咗遊行，避免引起懷疑，要晚飯前返去。<br />\n<br />\n我同佢講，與父母溝通的嘢要慢慢黎，佢答：我已經放棄咗啦。<br />\n<br />\n點解我們的下一代，連去遊行都要鬼鬼祟祟？"}]}